snippet.title: Mathematics II - VC 4000
snippet.description: The second Mathematics game for the Interton. This time with both multiplication and division. This game gets pretty hard when you get into it. You can create complex calculations with up to four numbers with three digits, and combine any calculus method. Definately the second level of mathematics for this console. Blogpost: http://retro-spill.blogspot.com/2014/02/mathematics-ii-vc-4000.html
